com.unvired.sync.notifier
Class DataNotification

java.lang.Object
  com.unvired.sync.notifier.DataNotification

public class DataNotification
extends java.lang.Object

Data notification is an object returned by the NotificationListener to notify data changes related to the business entities. Data notification provides the name of the business entity, action type (add, modify or delete) and the local identifier of the business entity header.
